contentText.text: Howdy everyone!!! Happy ALMOST 2024!!!!!!!!!!!! My final video of the year is a MASSIVE BLOOPER VIDEO - definitely the longest one we've ever had! However, we're going to give Denis a bit more time to finish it up, so it'll be posted tomorrow!! :) WOO WOO!!!

She’s backkkkkkk ~ Oh Daisy. It was nice and calm for a while, wasn't it... 💙

While doing the phone ringing foley, I had to dig back into my box of ANCIENT RELICS (flip phones lol) and find one that would actually turn on so that I could use it as a sound effect that wasn't insanely loud/disruptive hahah. It was... hard. 
Anyone else have the Envy phone??? I used to type like a SPEEED DEMON on that thing - and I would hide it in my desk at school and text without looking LMFAO -

Ya know, ’tis TRULY the season because my brain is all over the place, so much so that I didn’t even realize my microSD card on my audio mixer was ABOUT TO BE COMPLETELY FULL and it ended up ✨stopping the recording✨ after the few min of my Chill With Me video 🫠

BUT we got back up and refilmed the missing parts anyway LOLLLL -  sometimes u just lay on the floor for a minute ok ~

The 3DIO is BACK…and I guess I can honestly say better than ever??? It is still very far from my favorite mic, but I didn't think it was tooooo bad in my Least Favorite Triggers video! I am still personally undecided what my least favorite trigger in that video was though... 😂

What were some of the triggers that you either loved or hated?! I’m so curious to know how everyone feels about them!

WOOWHEEEE where do I even begin with the Fastest Christmas BTS? 

This video took SO long to make because of all of the different costumes and backdrops, but I had so much fun script writing and filming it! 🎄 ...and let me tell you...the studio cleanup was INTENSE. 

Surprisinglyyyyy I only had to make one new purchase for this video which was the little red trucks hauling Christmas trees ornaments…I guess I have finally accumulated enough decorations over the years to create SEVEN different sets!

Which one of these new characters would you want to see make an appearance next year? 👀

Back with some more behind the scenes for my latest Alien video! I hope you love OC videos as much as I do…especially when Fleeb Florb makes an appearance! 😁🛸

For the Fleeb and ~Beyoncé~ scene (SURPRISEEEE they were both me!), I put texture blocks on the ground and tape on the walls so I knew exactly where to stand and look! It only took about mmmmm 10 retakes…but WE GOT THERE!

Hi everyone!~ I decided it might be fun to start posting some fun facts/behind the scenes of videos as they're coming out! 😄

My latest video is the THIRD part of my tattoo journey! I'd love to know if you have any tattoos, or if you don't, if you would ever get one!
